summary: This is an email from July 3, 2019, regarding a subpoena rider (Subp Rider) related to the Division of Corporations in Albany. The subject concerns corporate entities 'Maple Inc' and 'Nine East 71st Street Corporation', and the email includes an attachment of the subpoena rider document.

events.title: Subpoena Rider Issuance/Transmission
events.description: An email is sent regarding a subpoena rider (Subp Rider) related to corporate entities Maple Inc and Nine East 71st Street Corporation, with the rider document attached.

keyFacts: The document is an email dated July 3, 2019, concerning a legal subpoena rider.
The subject of the subpoena rider involves two corporate entities: 'Maple Inc' and 'Nine East 71st Street Corporation'.
The location 'Nine East 71st Street' is referenced, which is a known property associated with Jeffrey Epstein in New York City.
The email includes an attachment titled 'NEW_YORIC_DEPARTMENT_OF_STATE_Subp_Rider Jeffity_Epstein_2.docx', indicating a misspelling of 'Jeffrey Epstein'.
The correspondence is directed to/from entities related to the New York Department of State's Division of Corporations.
